    <h2>What ICAO says about OJTIs</h2>

    <p>Before we start going through the requirements for practical
        instructors in the European environment, let’s take a look at what the
        ICAO documents says about instructors.</p>

    <p class="ians-text-instruction">Select each document cover to read about
        it:</p>

