    <p>We are now going to look at each aspect in more detail.</p>

    <h3>Requirements to obtain the endorsement</h3>

    <p>These requirements are <strong>similar</strong> for both endorsements
        (<strong>two years experience</strong> operating an ATCO licence and
        successful completion of a <strong>practical</strong> instructional
        technique course) with the major difference being that OJTIs need a
        <strong>valid ATC Licence</strong> (exercised at least two years
        immediately prior the application) and associated <strong>unit
          endorsement</strong>.
      </p>

