    <h3>Conditions/requirements to exercise the
        endorsement(s)</h3>

    <p>These are similar as well: <strong>two years experience</strong> in the
        rating they will instruct in for both endorsements but in the case of
        OJTI it is strengthened with a requirement for <strong>six months
          immediately previous</strong> experience in the unit endorsement where
        they will be instructing. Whereas this requirement is ‘softened’ for the
        STDI endorsement, so as to enable STDIs to instruct in the <strong>basic
          training</strong> for any rating and in the rating training for
        similar ratings. The requirement to <strong>practice instructional
          skills</strong> appropriate to the rating held is
        similar as well.</p>

  </div>

