    <h3>Requirements to maintain the endorsements</h3>

    <p>These are also <strong>similar</strong> for both OJTIs and STDIs
        (refresher training on practical instructional skills) with 
        <strong>additional refresher training</strong> on current operational
        practices for STDIs to compensate (partly) for the lack of current expereince (that an operational OJTI gains simply by having a valid ATCO licence).
      </p>

  </div>

