    <h3>Requirements for renewal of expired endorsements</h3>

    <p>These are almost the same. The differences are:</p>

    <ol class="list-inside list-decimal">
      <li>the OJTI needs to have a valid ATCO licence and</li>
      <li>there is a possibility for OJTIs to exchange their OJTI endorsement
          for an STDI endorsement in circumstances where their ATCO licence
          and/or associated unit endorsements validity expires.</li>
    </ol>

    <p>There is a further requirement for STDIs to have <strong>refresher
          training on current operational practises</strong>.</p>

  </div>

